    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">What is Verbling?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Verbling is an online language learning marketplace founded in 2011. Unlike some competitors, Verbling focuses specifically on live conversation lessons with professional tutors. The platform connects you with native English speakers from countries like the United States, United Kingdom, Canada, and Australia.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">What makes Verbling different is its "Verbling Flex" feature. This allows you to book instant lessons with any tutor who is currently available. If you have 30 minutes free right now, you can start learning immediately — no advance booking required.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">The platform also offers "Verbling Go" — a group class option where multiple learners join a single session. This can be a cost-effective way to practice English with native speakers while meeting other learners from around the world.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Pricing</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Verbling uses a credit-based system. You purchase credits first, then spend them on lessons. This gives flexibility, but it can feel less straightforward than subscription models.</p>
    
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
